&iacute; z&nbsp;oblasti hudebn&iacute; v&yacute;chovy. Sbormistryně, lektorka ČOS.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>','2014-12-31',0,0,1,0),
